<c74object name='sp.descriptorreplace' category='' module='SP-Tools'>
    <digest>Replace descriptors from descriptor list or buffer
</digest>
    <description>Replace descriptors from descriptor list or buffer.
</description>
    <discussion><h4><openfilelink filename="SP-Tools Overview.maxpat">Open the Overview Patch</openfilelink></h4>
The <o>sp.descriptorreplace</o> object takes incoming descriptors (as list or buffer) from <o>sp.descriptors~</o>/<o>sp.descriptorframe</o> and replace any of the four main descriptors within it (loudness, centroid, flatness, and pitch).
</discussion>

	<metadatalist>
		<metadata name='author'>Rodrigo Constanzo, Flucoma Project</metadata>
		<metadata name='tag'>Machine Learning</metadata>
		<metadata name='tag'>Audio Analysis</metadata>
		<metadata name='tag'>Onset Detection</metadata>
		<metadata name='tag'>Corpus Playback</metadata>
	</metadatalist>

